nsmitted to humans through the bite of infected mosquitoes.\", \"from\": 5236, \"to\": 5347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dengue fever\", \"from\": 5236, \"to\": 5248}, {\"ngram\": \"break-bone fever\", \"from\": 5264, \"to\": 5280}, {\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5306}, {\"ngram\": \"the bite\", \"from\": 5315, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"infected mosquitoes\", \"from\": 5327, \"to\": 5346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the World Health Organization (WHO), symptoms of infection include high fever, severe headaches, body aches, nausea, vomiting, and rash.\", \"from\": 5349, \"to\": 5498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Health Organization\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5391}, {\"ngram\": \"symptoms\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5407}, {\"ngram\": \"infection\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5420}, {\"ngram\": \"high fever\", \"from\": 5429, \"to\": 5439}, {\"ngram\": \"severe headaches\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5457}, {\"ngram\": \"body aches\", \"from\": 5459, \"to\": 5469}, {\"ngram\": \"nausea\", \"from\": 5471, \"to\": 5477}, {\"ngram\": \"vomiting\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These symptoms typically occur four to 10 days after infection.\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These symptoms\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5514}, {\"ngram\": \"infection\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the symptoms usually improve within one to two weeks, some individuals might develop severe dengue, which can be fatal in extreme cases.\", \"from\": 5565, \"to\": 5707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the symptoms\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5583}, {\"ngram\": \"one to two weeks\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5623}, {\"ngram\": \"some individuals\", \"from\": 5625, \"to\": 5641}, {\"ngram\": \"severe dengue\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme cases\", \"from\": 5693, \"to\": 5706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, many dengue infections are asymptomatic or result in only mild illness.\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many dengue infections\", \"from\": 5716, \"to\": 5738}, {\"ngram\": \"only mild illness\", \"from\": 5769, \"to\": 5786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the heightened alert and registered cases in the Paris region, those attending the event need to take precautions to avoid getting infected, officials have said.\", \"from\": 5789, \"to\": 5956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5844, \"end\": 5849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996257429, \"rank\": 3.743822692887341e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heightened alert and registered cases\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 5883}, {\"ngram\": \"precautions\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5908}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 5936, \"to\": 5945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the best way to prevent dengue fever is by avoiding mosquito bites, there issome WHO-recommended adviceto follow to protect against dengue.\", \"from\": 5958, \"to\": 6103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6016, \"end\": 6024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mosquito\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.901732787155048e-22, \"text\": \"mosquito\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mosquito\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mosquito\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best way\", \"from\": 5964, \"to\": 5976}, {\"ngram\": \"dengue fever\", \"from\": 5988, \"to\": 6000}, {\"ngram\": \"dengue\", \"from\": 6096, \"to\": 6102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wear protective clothing:Choose long-sleeved shirts, long pants, socks, and shoes to cover as much of the body as possible.\", \"from\": 6105, \"to\": 6228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"protective clothing\", \"from\": 6110, \"to\": 6129}, {\"ngram\": \"long-sleeved shirts\", \"from\": 6137, \"to\": 6156}, {\"ngram\": \"long pants\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6168}, {\"ngram\": \"socks\", \"from\": 6170, \"to\": 6175}, {\"ngram\": \"shoes\", \"from\": 6181, \"to\": 6186}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 6207, \"to\": 6215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Use mosquito repellents:Apply insect repellents containing DEET, Picaridin or IR3535 to exposed skin and clothing.\", \"from\": 6230, \"to\": 6344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mosquito repellents\", \"from\": 6234, \"to\": 6253}, {\"ngram\": \"insect repellents\", \"from\": 6260, \"to\": 6277}, {\"ngram\": \"DEET\", \"from\": 6289, \"to\": 6293}, {\"ngram\": \"Picaridin\", \"from\": 6295, \"to\": 6304}, {\"ngram\": \"IR3535\", \"from\": 6308, \"to\": 6314}, {\"ngram\": \"skin\", \"from\": 6326, \"to\": 6330}, {\"ngram\": \"clothing\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Use screen windows:Ensure that windows and doors are properly screened to keep mosquitoes out.\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Use screen windows\", \"from\": 6346, \"to\": 6364}, {\"ngram\": \"windows\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6384}, {\"ngram\": \"doors\", \"from\": 6389, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"mosquitoes\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Use mosquito coils and vaporizers:These could be particularly effective in reducing mosquito populations indoors.\", \"from\": 6442, \"to\": 6555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mosquito coils\", \"from\": 6446, \"to\": 6460}, {\"ngram\": \"vaporizers\", \"from\": 6465, \"to\": 6475}, {\"ngram\": \"mosquito populations indoors\", \"from\": 6526, \"to\": 6554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, if infection still occurs, people are recommended to rest, drink plenty of liquids, and use paracetamol for pain relief.\", \"from\": 6559, \"to\": 6688, \"entitie